      "title": "Fertilizer ship arrives",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Urea fertilizer ship given by the Government of India reached the port of Colombo at 11.00 am today",
        "The ship named MV-ELEEN ARMONIA carrying 40,000 metric tons of the 65,000 metric tons of fertilizer arrived at the port of Colombo."
      ],
